Wasu 'yan majalisar Wales sun yi takaici game da shawarar da aka yi na canza sunansa zuwa MWP (Wallisyan majalisar).
An yi wannan muhawara ne a kan shirin canja sunan majalisa zuwa 'yan majalisar Wales.'
