Wani shark ya yi wa wani ɗan shekara 13 rauni a wani jirgin ruwa mai kama da lobster a California
Wani shark ya kai hari kuma ya raunana wani yaro mai shekara 13 a ranar Asabar a lokacin da yake yin farautar raƙuman ruwa a California, a ranar farko ta kakar raƙuman ruwa, jami'an sun ce.
Wannan harin ya faru ne jim kadan bayan karfe 7 na safe kusa da Beacon's Beach, Encinitas.
Chad Hammel ya shaida wa KSWB-TV a San Diego cewa ya yi ruwa da abokai na kusan rabin sa'a lokacin da ya ji yaron yana kuka don taimako, sannan ya yi jirgi zuwa gare shi tare da wani rukuni don ya taimake shi ya fita daga cikin ruwa.
Hammel ya ce da farko ya yi tunanin cewa abin farin ciki ne kawai domin ya kama wani lobster, amma daga baya ya lura cewa yaron yana ihu "An yi mini cizon sauro"!
An cije ni!
Hammel ya kwatanta abin da ya gani sa'ad da ya kai yaron.
"Na yi kira ga kowa ya fita daga cikin ruwa: 'Akwai wani shark a cikin ruwa!' " in ji Hammel.
An kai yaron ta hanyar jirgin sama zuwa asibitin Rady Children a San Diego, inda aka shigar da shi cikin mawuyacin hali.
Ba a san irin sharkin da ya kai wannan hari ba.
Wani mai ceton rayuka, Capt. Larry Giles, ya bayyana a wata sanarwa da ya yi wa manema labarai cewa an ga wani shark a yankin makonni da suka gabata, amma an ce ba shi da haɗari.
Giles ya ƙara da cewa wanda aka kashe ya ji rauni sosai a saman gungumen.
Hukumomi sun rufe hanyar shiga daga Ponto Beach a Casablad zuwa Swami's a Ecinitas na tsawon sa'o'i 48 don bincike da dalilai na tsaro.
Giles ya ce akwai nau'in sharks fiye da 135 a yankin, amma yawancin ba a ɗauke su da haɗari ba.
Sainsbury's na shirin shiga kasuwar kayan kwalliya ta Burtaniya
Sainsbury's tana gasa da Boots, Superdrug da Debenhams don yin amfani da kayan shafawa kamar manyan kantunan kaya, wanda ke tallafawa ta hanyar masu ba da shawara.
A wani ɓangare na babban shiri na samun rabon kaya a kasuwar kwalliyar Burtaniya, wanda aka kiyasta a £2.8 biliyan, wanda ya ci gaba da girma yayin da tallace-tallace na tufafi da kayan gida suka ragu, za a gwada waɗannan manyan sassan kwalliya a shaguna 11 a duk faɗin ƙasar kuma za a tura su zuwa wasu shaguna a shekara mai zuwa idan an tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan zuba jari a cikin kayan shafawa ya fito ne daga bukatar manyan kantuna su yi amfani da sararin samaniya da aka yi amfani da shi don TVs, microwaves da kayan gida.
Sainsbury's ta ambata cewa za ta ninka kundin kayan kwalliyarta ta samar da kayayyaki har zuwa 3000, ciki har da sun hada da kamfanoni kamar Revlon, Essie, Tweezerman da Dr. PawPaw a karon farko.
Ƙungiyoyin L'Oréal da Maybelline da Burt's Bees da ke akwai yanzu za su sami ƙarin sarari tare da wuraren alama kamar na shagunan kamar Boots.
Ƙungiyar manyan kantuna tana sake ƙaddamar da kayan kwalliyar ta Boutique don yawancin kayayyakin su bi ƙa'idodin vegan, wani abu da matasa masu siye ke ƙara buƙata.
Bugu da ƙari, kantin sayar da turare mai suna The Fragrance Shop zai gwada tallace-tallace a shagunan Sainsbury's guda biyu, wanda na farko ya buɗe a Croydon, kudancin London a makon da ya gabata.
Cinikin kan layi da kuma sauya salon cin abinci zuwa ƙananan adadin yau da kullum a shagunan da ke kusa ya sa manyan kantuna yanzu suna bukatar su yi ƙoƙari sosai don su rinjayi abokan ciniki su ziyarci shagunan su.
Mike Coupe, shugaban zartarwa na Sainsbury's, ya ce shagunan za su zama kamar manyan kantuna a yayin da babbar shagon ke ƙoƙarin yaƙi da shagunan rangwame na Aldi da Lidl da ƙarin ayyuka da kayayyakin da ba abinci ba.
Sainsbury's ta kasance tana sanya wuraren sayar da Argos a ɗaruruwan shaguna, kuma ta kuma sanya jerin Habitats, tun da ta sayi duka sarkar biyu shekaru biyu da suka gabata, kuma ta ce hakan ya ƙarfafa tallace-tallace na kayayyakin sayarwa kuma ya sa sayayya ta fi riba.
Ƙoƙarin da kamfanin ya yi na sabunta kayan shafawa da kuma kantin magani ya gaza.
Sainsbury's ta yi ƙoƙari ta yi haɗin gwiwa da Boots a farkon shekarun 2000, amma dangantakar ta ƙare bayan jayayya game da rarraba kudaden shiga na shagunan kiwon lafiya a manyan kantunan su.
Wannan sabon dabarar ta zo ne bayan Sainsbury's ta sayar da kantin magani na 281 a shekara uku da ta shige ga Celesio, mai sayar da kantin sayar da kayayyaki na Lloyds Pharmacy, a kan fam miliyan 125.
Kamfanin ya ce Lloyds za ta shiga cikin shirin ta wajen ƙara manyan shagunan da ke da manyan kayayyakin fata kamar La Roche-Posay da Vichy a cikin shaguna huɗu.
Paul Mills-Hicks, darektan kasuwanci na Sainsbury's, ya ce: "Mun canja yanayin da kuma yanayin sassanmu na kayan shafawa don mu ba abokan cinikinmu yanayi mai kyau.
Mun kuma saka hannun jari wajen horar da abokan aiki da suka ƙware, waɗanda za su kasance a shirye su ba da shawara ga abokin ciniki.
An tsara jerin kayayyakinmu don su dace da dukan bukatunmu, kuma yanayi mai kyau da kuma wurare masu kyau sun sa mu zama wurin sayar da kayayyakin ado da ba za a iya jurewa ba da ke karya tsoffin hanyoyin yin sayayya".
