An kwatanta wannan kasuwancin da Gwyneth Paltrow ta yi da Goop kuma an yi hasashen cewa zai ninka dukiyar Willoughby, wanda aka kiyasta a fam miliyan 11.
Yayin da Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ya sanar a shafinsa na Instagram cewa zai bar Truly, Jones yana tashi zuwa wani gidan hutu a ƙasashen waje.
