Ƙari ga haka, zai iya nufin ƙarshen abokantaka ta dindindin.
Willoughby, wadda take da 'ya'ya uku, da mijinta Dan Baldwin sun kasance kusa da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp shekaru goma da suka shige.
Willoughby ya kirkiro Truly tare da Capp a shekarar 2016 kuma Jones, mai shekaru 52, ya shiga aikin a matsayin shugaban a watan Maris.
