Amma a yanzu, yanayi mai zafi a Tekun Fasifik yana soma aukuwa a arewacin Amurka, kuma yayin da yake gabatowa zuwa yankin Baja California, ruwan sama mai suna Rosa, wanda yanzu ya zama guguwar ruwan sama, zai fara tura zafi mai zafi zuwa arewacin yankin kudu maso yammacin Amurka.
A ranar Litinin, za a iya samun ruwan sama mai tsawo har zuwa millimeters 25 a wasu yankunan Mexico.
