Kavanaugh, a cikin shaidar da ta yi zafi, ya ce yana da tabbaci cewa ba haka ba ne.
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20.4 ne suka halarci taron, kamar yadda Nielsen ta nuna a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya lissafa matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a tashoshin CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a riga an ba da lambobin sauran tashoshin da suka watsa shi ba, irin su PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen tana da wahalar auna yawan masu sauraro daga masu kallon shirye-shirye a ofisoshin.
Don a yi la'akari da hakan, matakin da ake sauraronsa yana kama da na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa na Amirka ko kuma na bikin Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu sharhi suka ba da goyon baya mai ƙarfi ga nadin Kavanaugh, ya jagoranci dukkan tashoshin talabijin tare da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron da ya ɗauki tsawon yini, in ji Nielsen.
A cikin jerin sunayen, ABC ta zo na biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
Bayan haka, CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1 da NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 da CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52, Nielsen ta ce.
