Erdogan ya samu karbuwa a Cologne
Murmushi ya yi yawa a ƙarƙashin sama mai launin shuɗi a ranar Asabar (29 ga Satumba) lokacin da shugabannin Turkiyya da Jamus suka taru don karin kumallo a Berlin.
