Daruruwan masu zanga-zangar adawa da Erdogan, da yawa daga cikinsu Kurdawa ne, sun kuma saurari jawabin, suna yi wa shugaban kasar ba'a game da manufofinsa da kuma shawarar gwamnatin Jamus ta karbe shi a kasar.
Taron da ake yi a kan 'yan adawa ya nuna halin raba gardama na wani baƙo da wasu 'yan Jamus suka yi la'akari da shi jarumi kuma wasu suka ƙi shi a matsayin mai mulkin kai.
