Johnny English ya sake yin harin - fim din leken asiri mai ban tsoro tare da Rowan Atkinson
Yanzu yana da kyau a nemi ma'anar Brexit a kowane sabon fim da ke da ɗanɗano na Burtaniya, kuma wannan ya zama kamar yana aiki ne ga sabon fitowar fim ɗin wasan kwaikwayo da fim ɗin Johnny English, wanda aka fara a 2003 tare da "Johnny English" kuma aka dawo da shi zuwa rayuwa a 2011 tare da "The Return of Johnny English".
Shin, wannan baƙar magana game da mugunta da muke yi a kanmu ita ce sabuwar damar fitarwa ga al'ummarmu?
Ko ta yaya, Johnny English, wanda ba shi da iko, da idanunsa da suka yi tawaye da kuma fuskarsa da ta fi ƙarfin hali ya sami izininsa na ƙirƙirar rikice-rikice, an sake sabunta shi a karo na biyu - da sunansa ya nuna, fiye da kome, cewa wannan babban zane ne na ban dariya wanda aka tsara don 'yan wasan kwaikwayo na cinikin Turanci.
Shi ne, ba shakka, wani ɗan sanda mai zaman kansa wanda duk da irin wannan sha'awarsa na yin ado, yana da wani abu na Cloiseau, wani ɗanɗano na Mr. Bean, da kuma wani abu daga cikin mutumin da ya ba da gudummawa da wata alama ɗaya ga taken fim din "Moments of Glory" a bikin buɗe gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Bugu da ƙari, halinsa ya dogara ne da ɗan tafiya na duniya da kuma mutum mai ban mamaki wanda Atkinson ya taka rawa a cikin tallan TV don Barclaycard, wanda ya bar rikici a cikin hanyarsa.
Akwai wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa a wannan sabon fitowar JE.
Na yi farin ciki da ganin Johnny English yana zuwa kusa da wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu yana ɗauke da kayan kwalliya na zamani, tare da ƙuƙwalwar rotor da ke yin sautin ƙararrawa a kai tsaye a kan helmet.
A bayyane yake cewa Atkinson yana da basira ga wasan kwaikwayo, amma yanayin da ya dace yana da rauni kuma yana da ban mamaki, musamman idan aka yi la'akari da cewa shirye-shiryen fina-finai masu "ainihin" kamar 007 da Mission Impossible yanzu suna ba da tabbacin wasan kwaikwayo a matsayin kayan aiki.
Mun yi tunanin cewa ban dariya na yara ne ba manya ba, kuma a ganina, baƙon al'amuran Johnny English ba su da hankali sosai kamar lambobin Atkinson na fim ɗin da ba a yi magana ba a cikin Bean.
Yanzu, abin da ya fi muhimmanci shi ne cewa Birtaniya ta shiga cikin matsala mai tsanani.
Wani dan fashin kwamfuta ya shiga cikin hanyar leken asiri ta Birtaniya, yana bayyana ainihin dukkan jami'an Birtaniya a filin don jin tsoron jami'in sabis, wani muhimmin matsayi ga Kevin Eldon.
Wannan shi ne ƙarshen firaministan da ke nuna wani mutum mai ban sha'awa da rikici, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga rashin shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson ta yi iyakar ƙoƙarinta a wannan rawar da ta tuna da halin Theresa May, amma labarin bai ba da kayan aiki da yawa ga manyan jiragen sama ba.
Masu ba da shawara a cikin asusun sirri sun gaya mata cewa tun da aka yi wa dukan jami'an da ke aiki alkawari, dole ne ta cire wani daga aikin.
Kuma wannan mutumin shi ne Johnny English, wanda yanzu yake aiki a matsayin malamin makaranta mai kyau, amma yana koyar da darasi na yau da kullum game da yadda ake yin leken asiri: ga wasu kididdiga masu ban sha'awa, domin English yana ba mu makarantar leken asiri kamar fim din "School of Rock".
An kai English da sauri Whitehall don karɓar umarnin gaggawa kuma ya sake haɗuwa da mataimakinsa mai wahala Bough, rawar da Ben Miller ya sake takawa.
Bough yanzu ya zama mutum ne mai aure, wanda ya sha'awar kwamandan jirgin ruwa mai saukar ungulu, wani hali mai ban tsoro wanda Vicki Pepperdine ta yi amfani da shi a wani lokaci.
Don haka, Batman da Robin na bala'in a cikin Sirrin Mai Girma na sarautarsa sun dawo cikin aiki, suna fuskantar kyakkyawar mace mai ban tsoro Ophelia Bulletova, wanda Olga Kurylenko ta buga.
Amma a yanzu haka, firaministan yana cikin haɗari da mai ba da shawara mai ban sha'awa na biliyan na fasaha wanda ke da'awar zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Burtaniya: Jason Volta, mai ban tsoro, wanda Jake Lacy ya buga.
English da Bough sun fara tafiya da ba'a da ba'a: sun yi wa kansu sutura kamar ma'aikatan tebur, sun ƙone gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai ban sha'awa, sun haifar da rikice-rikice ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwa mai daraja na Volta, kuma English ya haifar da lalata mai tsabta yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da tabarau na gaskiya na gaskiya don sanin abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Hakika, an yi dukan tashoshin da aka yi da wannan shirin na ƙarshe, amma duk da haka, kamar yadda yake da kyau da kuma guguwa, an shirya wannan wasan don yara da yawa.
