Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun gaya wa "60 Minutes" ko binciken FBI akan Kavanaugh zai iya sa su canza ra'ayinsu ko a'a
Binciken FBI game da zargin da ake yi wa Alkalin Brett Kavanaugh ya jinkirta zaben karshe na nadin shi a kotun koli na akalla mako guda, yana tayar da tambayoyi game da ko sakamakon zai iya sa Sanatocin Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka yi a ranar Lahadi, mai ba da rahoto ga "60 Minutes" Scott Pelley ya tambayi Sanatocin Republican John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham ko FBI za ta iya gano wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya nuna cewa ya fi abokinsa a Carolina ta Kudu a fili.
"Ina nufin, ba shakka", ya ce Kennedy.
"Na ce lokacin da na je wurin sauraron, na ce, na yi magana da Alkalin Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan wannan, lokacin da wannan zargi ya bayyana, kuma na tambaye shi, "ka yi haka?"
Ya kasance mai tsauri, mai ƙuduri, marar ƙidaya".
Amma, muryar Graham ba ta canja ba.
"Na yanke shawarar Brett Kavanaugh kuma za a bukaci yin tuhuma mai fashewa", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san abu daya: Brett ya yi wani abu mai ban mamaki", in ji Graham, yana magana ne game da Christine Blasey Ford.
"Kuma duk wanda ta ambata ba su iya tabbatar da shi.
Shekaru 36 da suka wuce.
Ba na ganin wani sabon abu da ya canja".
Shin, kun yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani taron kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke tattare da jerin taurari masu ban sha'awa waɗanda za su yi aiki a kan manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
A shekara ta bakwai, bikin na Global Citizen zai gayyaci dubban mutane zuwa babban filin tsire-tsire na Central Park, ba wai kawai don kallon wasan kwaikwayon kamar na Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don karfafa wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar taron: kawar da talauci mai tsanani ta 2030.
Bikin Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekara ta 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wani kungiya mai ba da shawara da ke fatan kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da shi.
Don samun tikitin kyauta don taron (sai dai idan suna son su biya tikitin VIP) masu kallo sun yi jerin ayyuka, ko "aiki", kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, kiran waya, ko duk wasu hanyoyi masu mahimmanci da ke taimakawa wajen wayar da kan jama'a game da burin kawar da talauci.
Amma, yaya Global Citizen ta samu nasara a cikin shekaru 12 da suka wuce wajen cim ma burinta?
Tunanin bayar da kyauta kyauta ga mutane hanya ce ta gaske ta rinjayar su su yi aiki, ko kuma wannan wani abu ne na "clicktivism" - ganin cewa yana da bambanci a sanya hannu kan wata takarda ta yanar gizo ko aikawa da tweet?
Kamfanin Global Citizen ya ce tun shekara ta 2011, ya yi rajistar fiye da miliyan 19 na "aiki" na masu goyon bayansa da suka matsa lamba don cimma wasu manufofi.
Kungiyar ta ce waɗannan ayyukan sun sa shugabannin duniya su sanar da alkawura da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37, kuma hakan zai shafi rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta ambaci alkawura 390 da sanarwa daga hannun jarinta, kuma aƙalla dala biliyan 10 da aka kashe ko aka tara sun riga sun biya.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka samu sun yi tasiri kai tsaye a kan kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Wasu daga cikin manyan alkawuran sun hada da The Power of Nutrition, wani haɗin gwiwa na Burtaniya wanda ke tattara masu saka jari da masu aiwatarwa da ke da himma wajen "taimaka yara su cika iyakar damarsu", wanda ya yi alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 35 ga Rwanda don taimakawa kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar. Wannan bayan ya karbi fiye da 4,700 tweets daga Citizens Global.
"Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa, da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar mu duka, za mu iya yin rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin takardar tarihi", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, ga taron jama'a a wani taro na raye-raye a London, a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce bayan da aka yi wa Birtaniya taƙama fiye da 5,000 don inganta abinci mai gina jiki na iyaye mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta ba da kuɗi ga wani shiri, Power of Nutrition, wanda zai shafi mata da yara miliyan 5 da ke kula da abinci mai gina jiki.
A amsar wata tambaya da ake yawan yi a shafin, "Me ya sa kake ganin za mu iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Jaridar Global Citizen ta ce: "Ta kasance hanya mai tsawo da kuma ta wahala - a wasu lokatai muna yin tuntuɓe kuma muna kasawa.
Amma kamar yadda manyan ƙungiyoyin kare hakkin bil'adama da na yaki da wariyar launin fata suka yi a baya, domin mu ne mafi iko a hade.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B da Janelle Monáe suna cikin masu yin wasan kwaikwayo a wannan shekara a New York, wanda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman suka gabatar.
Amurka za ta iya amfani da rundunar jiragen ruwa a matsayin "tashin kai" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Cikin Gida
"Idan ya cancanta", Washington na iya amfani da rundunar jiragen ruwa don hana makamashin Rasha isa kasuwannin, ciki har da na Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, a cewar Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa shigar da Rasha cikin Syria, musamman a inda ta gayyaci gwamnati ta halal, wani abin zargi ne don yin amfani da sababbin kasuwannin makamashi.
"Na yi imanin dalilin da ya sa suke cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya shi ne domin su yi niyyar yin amfani da wutar lantarki kamar yadda suke yi a Gabas ta Turai a kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
Kuma, a cewar shugaban, akwai hanyoyi da kuma hanyoyin da za a hana shi.
"Amurka tana da ikon yin amfani da rundunar jiragen ruwa don tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa suna buɗewa kuma idan ya cancanta, ta toshe don tabbatar da cewa ba a samun wutar lantarki a kasuwa ba", in ji shi.
Zinke yana magana da masu halarta a wani taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ake kira "Muryar Mai Amfani da Makamashi" a Amurka.
A jawabinsa, ya ci gaba da kwatanta hanyoyin Washington na dangantaka da Rasha da Iran, yana cewa suna da ainihin irin wannan.
