Elizabeth Warren za ta "yi zurfin bincike" kan yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020, sanata ta Massachusetts ta ce
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta "yi zurfin bincike" kan yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben na gaba.
A wani zance na jama'a a garin Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ya tabbatar da cewa zai yi la'akari da takararsa.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don su gyara gwamnatinmu da ba ta da kyau, kuma hakan ya haɗa da mace a matsayin babban mai kula", in ji The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi zurfin bincike a kan takarar shugaban kasa".
Warren ya yi sharhi a kan Shugaba Donald Trump a lokacin tattaunawar ta yau da kullum, yana cewa "yana kai kasar cikin mummunan tafarki".
"Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump yake yi wa dimokiradiyya", in ji ta.
Warren ya kasance mai sukar Trump da kuma babban kotun kasar Brett Kavanaugh.
A wani sakon Twitter a ranar Juma'a, Warren ya yi nuni da cewa "a bayyane yake muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin zaben".
Duk da haka, wani bincike da aka gudanar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu jefa kuri'a na Warren ba su yarda da ita ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa a shekarar 2020.
Kashi 59 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a da suka yi tsammanin za su yi zabe a Massachusetts sun ce ba za ta yi takara ba, a cewar wani bincike da Cibiyar Bincike ta Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk/Boston Globe ta yi.
