Ramirez ya ce wanda aka nada a kotun koli ya fallasa gabobin jikinsu a lokacin da suka halarci wani biki a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekarun 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo mai fadi yana shirin kirkiro sabuwar intanet don yin gasa da Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kirkiro wani kamfani wanda yake son yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin wannan shahararren masanin fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke amfani da dandamali na Berners-Lee na bude tushen, Solid.
Wannan yana ba masu amfani damar yanke shawara a kan inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar wane bayani.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ta cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulki a duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", ya ce game da farawa.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don ba mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu "tushen bayanan sirri na kan layi", ko POD.
Wannan na iya ƙunsar jerin sunayen abokan hulɗa, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, ɗakin karatu na kiɗa, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna cikin burauzar guda kuma a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban sha'awa game da ajiyar bayanan sirri a kan layi shi ne cewa mai amfani ne kawai zai yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun irin wannan bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "Hanyar Bayanai don Ƙarfafa Mutum".
A cewar Shugaba John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce samar da albarkatu, hanyoyin da kuma basira don taimakawa wajen sa Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
A halin yanzu, Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu shirye-shiryen ciki da aka yi wa aiki a kan aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen aikin sa kai.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu kirkiro fasaha a duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen kansu na rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook da Google game da ko za a gabatar da cikakken canji inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su ke juyawa daga rana zuwa rana.
"Ba mu nemi izinin su ba".
A wani rubutu a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu wanda zai taimaka wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon yanar gizo da aka kirkira tare da Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a cikin muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na Intanet.
Ko da yake yana ƙaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa wanda ya kafa kuma ya jagoranci Ƙungiyar Yanar gizo ta Duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo, da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da wannan zamani na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: girmamawa ga limamin da aka ba da Victoria Cross a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
Limamin Ikilisiyar Ingila ne kaɗai ya sami lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya a matsayin mai yaƙi. An yi masa wannan lambar yabo a garinsa bayan shekara 100.
Lt. Col. Reverend Bernard Vann ya sami lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918 tare da kai hari ga Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani dan bindiga ya kashe shi kuma bai san cewa an ba shi babban darajar soja ta Birtaniya ba.
'Ya'yanta biyu sun saka wata lakabi a wani wurin shakatawa a Rushden, Northamptonshire, a ranar Asabar.
Ɗaya daga cikinsu, Michael Vann, ya ce "abin alama ne mai ban mamaki" cewa an gabatar da wannan lambar daidai shekaru 100 bayan abin da ya sa aka ba kakansa lambar yabo.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya jagoranci rundunarsa ta ƙetare tashar Saint-Quentin "cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai ƙarfi na bindigogi da bindigogi".
Sai ya gudu zuwa layin wuta kuma, "da ƙarfin hali", ya jagoranci layin gaba kafin ya kai hari kanana shi kaɗai kuma ya kashe sojoji uku na kwamitin.
Lt. Col. Vann an kashe shi ne ta hanyar dan wasan Jamus a ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, a little more than a month before the end of the war.
Michael Vann, mai shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa "abin da na sani ba zan taɓa daidaitawa ba, amma kuma darasi ne na tawali'u".
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun saka kambi na furanni bayan gangamin, wanda Brentwood Imperial Youth Band ta jagoranci.
Michael Vann ya ce "ya yi farin ciki sosai da ya halarci wannan zanga-zangar", kuma ya ƙara da cewa "ƙarfin wani jarumi na gaske yana nunawa ta wurin goyon bayan da mutane da yawa za su ba shi".
Masu sha'awar hada-hadar yaki sun tashi dare duka don kallon Bellator 206 maimakon kallon Porca Peppa
Ka yi tunanin wannan: Ka yi barci duk dare don ka kalli Bellator 206, cike da taurari, kuma a ƙarshe ka yi watsi da babban taron.
San Jose jerin sun hada da gwagwarmaya 13, tare da shida daga cikin manyan kungiyoyi, kuma ana nuna su a kai a kai a daren a Burtaniya, a Channel 5.
Da ƙarfe shida na safe, sa'ad da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald suke shirin yin gwagwarmaya, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamaki lokacin da aka canja murfin zuwa Pig Peppa.
Wasu ba su yi mamaki ba bayan sun farka da sassafe musamman don yaƙi.
Wani mai goyon baya a shafinsa na Twitter ya kwatanta sauyawar zuwa zane-zane na yara a matsayin "wani irin ban dariya mai ban dariya".
"Hukumar gwamnati ta ce ba su dace da sa'ar shida na safe ba, don haka sai suka canja wurin zuwa wani lokaci", in ji Dave Schwartz, mai kula da kasuwanci da sadarwa, sa'ad da aka bincika watsa shirye-shiryen.
"Daga Peppa, na sani".
Shugaban kamfanin Bellator, Scott Coker, ya ce kamfanin zai gyara jadawalin watsa shirye-shirye don ya haɗa da masu kallo na Burtaniya a nan gaba.
Coker ya ce: "Ina ganin cewa idan na yi tunani game da maimaitawa, zan iya magance matsalar.
