Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka afkawa birnin Palu a Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, jami'an sun ruwaito, inda ake sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Da yake an katse sadarwa, 'yan gudun hijira ba su iya samun wani bayani game da yankin Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu wanda ke kusa da tsakiyar girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya ne, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mazaunan 379,800 a cikin 2017.
Birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwa lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka faru.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A shekara ta 2017, yankin yana da mazaunan 299,200.
Fishing da kuma noma sune manyan ayyukan tattalin arziki na lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, musamman a yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Ana samun nickel a lardin, amma yawancin su suna Morowali, a bakin tekun Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, tsunami ya addabi Palu da Donggala sau da yawa, in ji hukumar kula da bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a birnin Donggala.
Wani tsunami ya kai ga yammacin birnin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin Pacific Ring of Seismic Fire kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh na Indonesia, a arewacin Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa gabar tekun kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 7.5 ta afka wa tsibirin Mentawai a gabashin Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsayi har zuwa mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai zurfi ya afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya, a Aceh, yana sa mutane su ji tsoro da kuma lalacewa domin sun tuna da mummunan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 2004.
A wannan lokacin, babu tsunami, amma mutane fiye da 100 ne suka mutu a ƙarƙashin rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ƙasa ta lalata dubban gine-gine, ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a zamance.
