An zargi Saipov mai shekara 30 da yin amfani da wata babbar mota da aka yi hayar ta Home Depot don kai hari a watan Oktoba a kan titin babur a West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, inda ya yi karo da matafiya da kuma masu hawa keke.
Don a yi amfani da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara za su bukaci su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe wadanda suka mutu takwas "da gangan" kuma ya yi mummunan rauni "da gangan", a cewar sanarwar da ke neman hukuncin kisa, da aka yi a yankin kudancin New York.
