Makonni bayan harin, wani kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifuffuka 22, ciki har da laifuffuka takwas na kisan kai a cikin ayyukan aikata laifuka, wanda Ofishin Sakataren Jama'a ke amfani da shi a lokuta na aikata laifuka, da kuma laifin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da ya dace da shi", kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya kashe shi a matsayin "m, mugun da kuma lalatacce".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi rauni, ya yi rauni kuma ya rasa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne na kasar Argentina.
Shekara goma da ta shige, yankin kudancin New York bai nemi hukuncin kisa ba don zargin da ake yi.
