Warren yana shirin "tunanin gaske" game da takarar shugaban kasa
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta "tambaya takarar shugaban kasa sosai" bayan zaben watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa 'yar majalisa ta Democrat ta Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomar ta a wani muhawara a jihar a ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, tana neman sake zabar zaben a watan Nuwamba a kan ɗan majalisar Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda ya yi aiki tare da Trump a yakin neman zaben 2016 a Massachusetts.
An yi hasashen cewa zai iya fuskantar Trump a shekarar 2020.
Taron da ya faru a yammacin Asabar a Holyoke shi ne karo na 36 da ya gana da masu jefa kuri'a a tsarin tattaunawa tun lokacin da Trump ya karbe mulki.
Wani mai halartar taron ya tambaye shi ko yana shirin neman shugabanci.
Warren ya amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da "mata za su je Washington su gyara matsalolin gwamnatinmu kuma hakan ya haɗa da mace a saman".
An kama shi a cikin kisan Wayde Sims, na LSU Tigers
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Louisiana, sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa an kama wani wanda ake zargi da kisan gillar da aka yi wa dan wasan kwallon kwando na LSU Tigers, Wayde Sims a ranar Juma'a.
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge sun sanar da kama Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, a wani taron manema labarai da ƙarfe 11 na safe.
'Yan sanda sun fitar da bidiyon harin a ranar Juma'a, suna neman taimako wajen gano mutumin da aka gani a cikin hotunan.
An kashe Sims, dan shekara 20, a kusa da harabar jami'ar Southern a safiyar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya sami kansa a cikin wuta, kuma ya mutu", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul a ranar Asabar ga 'yan jarida, a cewar 247sports.
Wani abokinsa ne Wayde ya yi wa'azi kuma Simpson ya harbe shi.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi kuma ya yarda ya kasance a wurin, yana riƙe da bindiga, yana yarda ya harbe Wayde Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da ya yi tsayayya ba kuma an kai shi ofishin 'yan sanda na East Baton Rouge Parish.
Sims, ɗan shekara 1,98 a Baton Rouge, ya buga wasanni 32 kuma ya zama ɗan wasa sau 10 a kakar wasa ta ƙarshe, yana da matsakaicin minti 17.4, maki 5.6, da kuma dawowa 2.9 a wasa.
Babban Kyautar Rasha: Lewis Hamilton ya zo gasar cin kofin duniya tare da nasara a kan Sebastian Vettel bisa ga umarnin tawagar
Daga lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya yi nasara a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar, ya bayyana sarai cewa umurnin da ake ba da wa 'yan wasa a Mercedes zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a tseren.
Bayan ya fita daga matsayi na farko, Bottas ya fara da kyau kuma ya bar Hamilton a baya yayin da yake kare matsayinsa a farkon kusurwoyi biyu, yana ba Vettel damar kai hari ga abokin aikinsa.
Vettel ya fara wasan kuma ya sa Hamilton ya fuskanci matsalar zirga-zirgar da ke tattare da ƙarshen rukuni, wanda zai iya zama mai yanke hukunci.
Mercedes ya tafi filin wasa bayan da ya yi kusa da Vettel, amma Hamilton ya wuce shi bayan da ya yi rikici, bayan da direban Ferrari ya bar cikin filin jirgin sama a hankali, yana fuskantar haɗarin gurfanawa bayan gyaran hanya biyu don kare kansa a karo na uku.
Max Verstappen ya fita daga ƙarshen layin kuma yana matsayi na bakwai a ƙarshen zagaye na farko a ranar haihuwarsa ta 21.
Ya jagoranci babban ɓangare na tseren, yana canza tayoyin da wuri, wanda zai ba shi damar yin sauri a ƙarshen, yana nufin ya wuce Kimi Raikkonen don kammala a matsayi na huɗu.
Ya zo wasan a zagaye na 44 amma bai samu nasarar inganta saurin sa ba a zagaye na takwas da suka gabata, wanda ya ba Raikkonen damar kammala a karo na hudu.
"Yana da wuya a rana domin Valtteri ya yi aiki mai ban mamaki a duk karshen mako kuma ya kasance mai gaskiya gentleman, barin ni wuce shi.
Ƙungiyar ta yi aiki mai kyau, wanda ya sa muka kasance a matsayi na farko biyu", in ji Hamilton.
Baƙar magana ta jiki
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya yi wa Sanata Dianne Feinstein ba'a a wani taron da ya yi a ranar Asabar saboda ta nace cewa ba za ta bayyana wata wasika daga Christine Blasey Ford ba da ke zargi Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a Kotun Koli, da cin zarafin jima'i.
Da yake jawabi a wani taron da aka yi a West Virginia, shugaban bai yi magana kai tsaye game da shaidar Ford a gaban Kwamitin Shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai ba, sai ya ce abin da ke faruwa a Majalisar Dattijai ya nuna cewa mutane "mara kyau ne, masu mugunta ne, kuma ba su da gaskiya".
"Ku ga abin da ke faruwa a majalisar dattawa a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan, ku ga fushin, ku ga yadda mutane suke mugunta, mugunta, da kuma ƙarya", in ji Trump.
"Idan muka ga bayanan da aka fitar da sakonnin da kuma lokacin da suka ce, 'Oh, ba ni ba ne.
Ba ni ba ne.
Ka tuna?
Dianne Feinstein, shin kai ne ka sa wannan ya faru?
Ka tuna da amsar da ta ba ka?
A'a, ba haka ba ne.
Ba na barin gudu.'
To, ku jira a can.
"Ba mu ba ne", in ji ta, ta yi koyi da sanatan.
Feinstein ya karbi wasikar da ke dauke da bayanan zargin da aka yi wa Kavanaugh da Ford ya aika a watan Yuli kuma ya yi gudun hijira a farkon watan Satumba, amma ya musanta cewa ya yi gudun hijira daga ofishinsa.
"Ban ɓoye zargin Dr. Ford ba, ban bayyana labarinta ba", Feinstein ya gaya wa Hukumar, kamar yadda The Hill ta ruwaito.
"Ta nemi na tsare sirri, kuma na yi biyayya da bukatarta".
Amma ƙin yarda da shi bai sa shugaban ya amince ba, wanda ya ce a taron da ya yi a ranar Asabar da dare: "Kun san abin da ya fi haka, wannan mummunan magana ce ta jiki.
