Da yake ci gaba da kare dan takarar kotun koli, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin mata uku, shugaban ya ba da shawarar cewa 'yan Democrat za su yi amfani da zargin a madadinsa.
"Suna da niyyar komawa mulki ta hanyar amfani da duk wata hanya.
Muna ganin mugunta, mugunta, ba kome ba ne wanda za su iya kaiwa, wanda za su yi tafiya don su sami iko da iko", in ji Shugaban, a cewar Mediaite.
Rukunin farko: Dundee Stars ta doke Belfast Giants 5-3
Patrick Dwyer ya ci raga biyu a raga a wasan Giants da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi nasara a ranar Jumma'a a wasan farko da suka yi da Belfast Giants, inda suka ci nasara da 5-3 a ranar Asabar a Dundee.
Giants sun samu ci gaba na farko na gol biyu tare da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun yi kusa da gida kafin Dwyer ya sake sa Giants a gaba.
François Bouchard ya yi kusa da Dundee kafin Luka Lundvald ya ci biyu ya tabbatar da nasarar tawagar.
Wannan shi ne karo na uku da aka yi wa Adam Keefe da ya ci nasara a ranar Juma'a da dare a Belfast, inda ya ci Dundee 2-1 a raga.
Wannan ne karo na hudu da suka yi a kakar wasa tsakanin kungiyoyin biyu, kuma Giants sun lashe wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya zira kwallo a minti na hudu (3:35) bayan Kendall McFaull ya taimaka, tare da David Rutherford yana kallon Beauvillier ya kara daukowa bayan minti hudu.
A cikin wata matsala ta farko, Sullivan ya sake sa tawagar gida ta yi wasa a karfe 1:10 na dare kafin Matt Marquardt ya ba da Cownie a karfe 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun kai ga farkon zangon farko a cikin jagorancin, yana zira kwallaye na biyu na dare a ƙarshen zangon farko.
A lokacin da aka sake shirya tawagar gida, Bouchard ya sake yin wasan da babbar kwallo a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun haɗa kai don taimakawa Nielsen ya jagoranci Dundee a wasan farko a ƙarshen karo na biyu, yana tabbatar da nasara ta hanyar zira kwallaye na biyar na ƙungiyar a tsakiyar karo na ƙarshe.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, za su karbi bakuncin Milton Keynes a wasan da zai zo a ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da jiragen sama ya mutu don taimakawa daruruwan fasinjoji su tsere daga girgizar kasa
An yi wa wani mai kula da jiragen sama a Indonesia yabo a matsayin jarumi bayan ya mutu don ya tabbatar da cewa jirgin sama da ke dauke da dubban fasinjoji zai tashi lafiya.
Mutane sama da 800 sun mutu kuma mutane da yawa sun ɓace bayan girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Jumma'a, ta haifar da tsunami.
Ƙarƙashin wutar lantarki yana ci gaba da mamaye yankin, yana barin mazauna da yawa a cikin rufin birnin Palu.
Duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun gudu don su ceci kansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung mai shekara 21 ya ƙi barin matsayinsa yayin da hasumiyar kula da jirgin ta yi ta ta tawaye a filin jirgin saman Mutiara Sis Al Jufri, a Palu.
Ya mai da hankali sosai don ya tabbata cewa jirgin Batik Air na 6321, wanda a lokacin yana kan hanya, ya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya tsallake daga hasumiyar iko, a gaban babban rushewar.
Ya mutu daga baya a asibiti.
Kakakin hukumar kula da jiragen sama ta Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin zai iya ceton daruruwan rayuka, in ji gidan talabijin na Australia ABC News.
Mun tura wani jirgin sama daga Balikpapan zuwa Kalimantan don a kwashe shi zuwa wani babban asibiti a wani gari.
Abin takaici, ya mutu a safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palu.
Ya daɗa: "Mun yi mamaki sosai da wannan labari.
Amma, hukumomi na tsoron cewa adadin mutuwar zai iya kai dubbai, suna cewa hukumar kula da bala'in kasar ta iyakance samun damar zuwa biranen Donggala, Sigi da Boutong.
"Rashin da ake yi yana ƙaruwa, tun da akwai gawawwakin da yawa da aka binne a cikin ramin da ba mu iya ceto ba tukuna", in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho.
Ruwa mai tsayi har zuwa mita shida ya lalata Palu, inda ake gudanar da jana'izar jama'a a ranar Lahadi.
Jiragen sama na kasuwanci da na soja suna kaiwa da taimakon jama'a da kayayyakin abinci zuwa wurin.
Wata mahaifiyar shekara 35 mai suna Risa Kusuma ta gaya wa Sky News: "Kowace minti na zuwa da motar asibiti da gawawwakin mutane.
Ruwa mai kyau ba ya samuwa.
Ana saɓon ƙananan kasuwanni a ko'ina".
Jan Gelfand, wanda ke kula da kungiyar agaji ta kasa da kasa a Indonesia, ya shaida wa CNN cewa: "Kungiyar agaji ta Indonesia tana tserewa a kan lokaci don taimakawa wadanda suka tsira, amma ba mu san abin da za mu samu ba.
Yanayin da muke ciki yanzu yana da ban tsoro, amma zai iya zama mafi muni".
Shugaban Indonesia, Joko Widodo ya isa Palu a ranar Lahadi. Majiyoyin CNN sun ce ya yi magana da sojojin kasar a wurin kuma ya ce:
"Ina rokon ku ku yi aiki dare da rana don kammala aikin kwashe mutane. Shin kun shirya?"
A farkon wannan shekara, girgizar ƙasa ta addabi tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 550.
Jirgin sama ya fadi a Micronesia: Air Niugini ta sanar da cewa wani mutum ya bace bayan jirgin ya fadi a tafkin
Kamfanin da ke kula da jirgin da ya fadi a wani kogin a Micronesia, Pacific, ya sanar da cewa mutum daya ya bace bayan ya sanar da cewa an ceto fasinjoji 47 da kuma ma'aikatan jirgin da ke cikin jirgin.
A wata sanarwa, kamfanin Air Niugini ya ce tun ranar Asabar da yamma ba ta iya tabbatar da inda wani namiji ya shiga ba.
Kamfanin yankin ya ce yana aiki tare da asibitoci, masu bincike da hukumomin yankin don gano mutumin.
A cewar wani rahoto da aka fitar a watan Janairun 2013, kamfanin jirgin sama ya bayyana cewa ya yi watsi da matakin da ya dauka na samar da jirgin sama.
Jiragen ruwa na gida sun taimaka wajen ceton sauran fasinjoji da kuma ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya fadi a cikin ruwa yayin da yake ƙoƙarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Tsibirin Chuuk.
Hukumomi sun ce a ranar Juma'a an kwantar da mutane bakwai a asibiti.
Kamfanin ya ce fasinjoji shida ne suka kasance a asibiti a ranar Asabar, dukansu suna da lafiya.
Har yanzu ba a san ainihin abin da ya sa aka faɗi ko kuma ainihin abin da ya faru ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama da na Amurka sun amince cewa jirgin ya kasa kaiwa kan hanya kuma ya yi bacci a cikin kogin.
Wasu shaidu sun yi zaton jirgin ya bar hanya.
Bill Jaynes, wani ɗan Amirka, ya ce jirgin yana zuwa ƙasa sosai.
Jaynes ya ce: "Wannan shi ne mafi kyau da ya faru.
Jaynes ya ce shi da wasu sun yi nasarar yin amfani da ruwa a cikin belinsu don su kai ga tashoshin gaggawa na jirgin da ke nutsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin sun firgita kuma suka soma ihu, kuma ya ji rauni a kai.
Rundunar Sojojin Amirka ta ce, ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa da ke aiki a wurin da ake gyara ruwa a kusa da wurin sun taimaka wajen ceton mutane ta wajen amfani da jirgin ruwa don su kai mutane ƙasa kafin jirgin ya faɗi zuwa zurfin mita 100.
Bisa ga bayanan da cibiyar tsaro ta jirgin sama ta tattara, a cikin shekaru biyu da suka gabata, mutane 111 sun mutu a hatsarin da aka yi da kamfanonin jiragen sama da ke rajista a PNG, amma babu wanda ya shafi Air Niugini.
Wani mai bincike ya bayyana tarihin abubuwan da suka faru a daren da aka kone wata mace da rai
A ranar Asabar ne ake kammala zargin a wani sabon shari'ar da aka yi wa wani mutum da ake zargi da kona mace a Mississippi a shekara ta 2014.
Paul Rowllet, mai bincike a Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amirka, ya ba da shaida na sa'o'i da yawa a matsayin masanin nazarin bayanai.
Ya bayyana wa alƙalan yadda ya yi amfani da bayanan wayar sa don yin rikodin motsi na wanda ake tuhuma Quintom Tellis, mai shekara 20, da wanda ake tuhuma Jessica Chamber, mai shekara 19, a daren da aka kashe ta.
A cewar jaridar Clarion Ledger, Rowlett ta ce ta samu bayanan wuri daga wayoyin salula da yawa da ke tabbatar da cewa Tellis yana tare da Chambers a daren da ya mutu, yana ƙaryata da bayanan da ta bayar a baya.
Bayan bayanan sun nuna cewa wayarka ta kasance tare da Chambers a lokacin da ya ce yana tare da abokinsa Michael Sanford, sai 'yan sanda suka je wurin Sanford.
Sanford ya shaida a ranar Asabar kuma ya bayyana cewa bai kasance a cikin gari a wannan rana ba.
Sa'ad da masu tuhuma suka tambaye shi ko Tellis yana faɗin gaskiya ne ta wajen cewa yana cikin motarsa a wannan daren, Sanford ya amsa cewa yana ƙarya ne domin motar tana Nashville".
Wani rashin jituwa a shaidar Tellis ya nuna cewa ya ce ya san Chambers kusan makonni biyu da suka gabata lokacin da ta mutu.
A cikin bayanan wayar salula sun nuna cewa sun san juna ne kawai mako guda da suka wuce.
Rowlett ta ce, wani lokaci bayan mutuwar Chambers, Tellis ya share saƙonnin rubutu da kira da kuma bayanan tuntuɓar Chambers daga wayarta.
