The High Breed: Menene hip hop mai hankali?
Wata ƙungiyar hip hop ta yi ƙoƙari ta canja yanayin da ke nuna rashin amincewa ta wajen cika waƙarsu da saƙonni masu kyau.
Ƙungiyar Bristol ta The High Breed ta ce hip hop ya koma baya daga tushen siyasa da kuma sukar zamantakewar.
