A cewar New York Post, lokacin da ta lura da rashin lafiyarta, Lynsey Plasco-Flaxman "mai ciki" ta kori Giselle Maurice da'awar rashin aikin da ta yi na baya na amaryar Afirka ta Amirka kuma tana jiran amaryar Filipino.
